   <body>
      <context>
         <p>The <uicontrol>Current Budget  Estimate</uicontrol> page provides a consolidated view of all items that are part of approved  budget estimate and all of its approved revisions.<note>If the project does not have any approved budget, then the <uicontrol>CURRENT BUDGET ITEMS</uicontrol> page is blank.</note>
         </p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>In the module menu, click <uicontrol>Projects</uicontrol>
            </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>PROJECTS</uicontrol> list page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the list page, double-click the required project, and in the navigation pane, expand the project folder.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol>Budget Management</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol>Current Budget </uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>CURRENT BUDGET ITEMS</uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
            <p>
               <fig product="PG_Screenshot">
                  <title>Current Budget Items Page</title>
                  <image href="../../Icons/Screenshots_Icons/Current_Budget.jpg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>Total Amount in $</uicontrol> field displays the sum of amounts of all items of the approved budget estimate and all of its revisions. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
